WEBVTT

00:11:27.720 --> 00:11:30.336
and that men and women,

00:11:30.360 --> 00:11:33.256
from blue-collar workers
to executive boardrooms

00:11:33.280 --> 00:11:37.656
were dealing with this range
of issues from harassment to assault,

00:11:37.680 --> 00:11:42.056
and that there were
elaborate systems in place

00:11:42.080 --> 00:11:45.376
that could be utilized
by the most powerful

00:11:45.400 --> 00:11:46.936
and the wealthiest --

00:11:46.960 --> 00:11:49.056
usually men in this country --

00:11:49.080 --> 00:11:53.336
to silence voices
that spoke out against that.

00:11:53.360 --> 00:11:57.616
And as I spoke to these
very brave sources who came forward --

00:11:57.640 --> 00:11:59.656
I wish I could take any credit for this,

00:11:59.680 --> 00:12:01.936
this was about sources
like Ashley, who spoke --